---
title: Plant-Based Crumbed Chick'n & Chermoula Wedges with Radish Salad & Plant-Based Mayo
description: Who says eating plant-based is boring? It's time to get excited for our crumbed chick'n – we've paired it with spiced baked
wedges and an radish salad for maximum flavour and fun. Don't forget the plant-based mayo for dipping!
